			<div class="content" id="post-content-1825708">
									

<p>I did not mean to imply that &quot;those who need&quot; were inferior, just that they would benefit best from a certain approach. Being green is not something to be ashamed of. At least not if one is trying to correct the condition.</p>
<p>But a person who, whether thru personality flaw or simple newness, has not yet internalized advice like this is a person who would benefit from language that is as plain and unambiguous as possible.</p>
<p>To be most effective, we must speak to the level where they are; and this is the &quot;101&quot; class material.</p>

