			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2243138">
									

<p>Oh. Then no, I don't see the use of that at all. I tend to prefer critique that indicates to me &quot;I've read your piece&quot; rather than &quot;I've read what other people wrote about your piece&quot;.</p>
<p>It may be an individual difference between authors though, so I feel I've said my piece on this matter.</p>

