<p>Thank you!<br />
I definitely plan to continue to write and will likely continue to write horror.<br />
Genuine feedback is very valuable and can sometimes be hard to find. I may not write SCPs, but I will always be looking for that kind of feedback.</p>
<p>Good luck with your drafts! I hope you publish one that you and the community are happy with.</p>

